  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">FYI, Iksar can swim up the waterfall to the right when you enter Nurga. I haven't tried the other one. Was able to do it twice last night, but the others with me couldn't do it until they were shrunk. Perhaps it is related to swimming skill rank (165 for me).<br>
