  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">I would like to add an item.  The item is "Niccolite".<br>
<br>
It drops off of a slave (slave is a magician--earth pet, but I believe I have seen both Burynai and Goblin slaves with mage pets).<br>
<br>
The spawn point of this mob is in the Spider area of Nurga (there is one cave where a slave always spawns, no other mobs.  *Usually* it is a mage, approx level 33--a bit above the Sleeping Ogre).  I have looted two Niccolites, and have seen more drop--they are common when the spawn is a mage, and sawn is about 10 min--whatever normal Nurga spawn is.  Item is no drop, 0.1 weight, no stats.  I looted it *several* months ago, the first time (about September/October 2000), and again in 01/01.  There is not one site that I could think of to search that mentions this item, but it is not rare (the mob is in such a place, that there is little to no reason to bother killing it, and if you are in that area of the dungeon, it prolly won't give you exp).<br>
<br>
I would like to see some site mention this item, in hopes of discovering it's purpose, and I find your site extremeley useful, so I submit it here.<br><br></td></tr>
