  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">This dungeon is one of the funnest I have ever been in! My first visit ever was about 2 weeks ago with a full group of level 30's. It was intense and a challenge the entire time since everything was yellow and red to us. We made it pretty far in until we got overwhelmed and our cleric gated out with me being the only one left to do CR it was about 2 hours clean up. Be prepared to spend sometime doing this right, and keep moving. With the new XP bonus added it should be awesome! And I have never seen a soul in there! But be aware, this zone is one way! Once you make the drop down the waterfall there is no turning back! A solid group of Level 33-36 could rock here! It's a beautiful looking dungeon too! Anytime you get to dive off a waterfall, go for it!<br><br></td></tr>
