  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">This is a good zone in IMHO.  The lack of most money, and the rarity of the drops are made up for my the rather common dropping of other things.  For example, I was there last night for only 45mins tops, and I picked up a black pearl, two peridots, an emerald, some blue stuff called Mt. death mineral salts, iksar blood, and other various GEMS.  It seems to me Verant did a GOOD job on this zone, they are in a mine, right?  Well then how would they get out and get money, instead the have gems that sell for a bit of pp!  Good Job verant, i'll be here till they are all green and i have all the loot out of this place :)  Nice drops too, have you seen that shield!<br><br></td></tr>
