  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">The sleeping ogre for monk epic quest turns into "trunt", lvl 59 I believe, after he is giving the necessary item. He is gullerback on steroids. He has a high magic resistance and when you get him down to low health he becomes enraged.<br>
<br>
Also, the sleeping ogre has a large aggro range, so don't engage him till your ready. And one last note, if you pull him, keep a eye, get as clost to him as you can to pull him, if you lose him he wanders off and suicides himself to prevent being pulled to zone. Spawn time is 3 hours if he suicides or you kill him.<br><br></td></tr>
