  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">one word for this zone WOW.  this has got to be some of the best exp ever. This place can easily be done with a group of 3 near lvl 40.  Chanter Cleric Warrior, or druid instead of cleric.  Minimal healing is needed if you use stun fighting. My group went on the burynai side and went through ever last one.  I ended up with 3/4 bubs of exp, and thats in lvl 40.  The other two people got  over a bub and a half of exp.  Just grab a map and move through areas as quickly as possible, resting safely in hallways.  Onle things that see through invis are spiders but they can be avoided by hugging walls. <br><br></td></tr>
